==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Heartedness
<hw>Heart"ed*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Earnestness; sincerity;
heartiness.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Clarendon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ See also the Note under <er>Hearted</er>. The analysis
of the compounds gives <xex>hard-hearted</xex> + -<xex>ness</xex>,
rather than <xex>hard</xex> + <xex>heartedness</xex>, etc.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hearten</ent>⟦br⟧
